::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

DeathScythe frowns as he flies toward the mountain range he had been heading 
for. There was a new bot on his scanners, heading south. He narrows his eyes, 
scanning the forest to get a more accurate location. He smiles evily, 
lowering altitude and heading toward the new bot.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus frowns, continuing to gallop through the forest. The bot he had been 
following was getting lower, almost landing in the forest. Ramulus speeds up, 
heading toward DeathScythe.
